2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses machine learning techniques such as deep neural networks and Markov random fields to estimate the crowd count. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses AI techniques such as deep learning and neural networks to solve the problem of crowd counting. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with analyzing and processing multimedia data (images) to estimate crowd count. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses neural networks to estimate the crowd count, which falls under the scope of neural computing.
